maica\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Jamaica\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Noah Lyles\", \"from\": 27, \"to\": 37}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic\", \"from\": 42, \"to\": 53}, {\"ngram\": \".005 seconds\", \"from\": 68, \"to\": 80}, {\"ngram\": \"the finish\", \"from\": 119, \"to\": 129}, {\"ngram\": \"an excruciatingly close sprint\", \"from\": 133, \"to\": 163}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The word \\\"Photo\\\" popped up on the scoreboard after Lyles and Thompson dashed to the line.\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 307, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The word\", \"from\": 218, \"to\": 226}, {\"ngram\": \"Photo\", \"from\": 228, \"to\": 233}, {\"ngram\": \"the scoreboard\", \"from\": 248, \"to\": 262}, {\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 269, \"to\": 274}, {\"ngram\": \"Thompson\", \"from\": 279, \"to\": 287}, {\"ngram\": \"the line\", \"from\": 298, \"to\": 306}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles paced the track with his hands draped over his head.\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 366, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 308, \"to\": 313}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 320, \"to\": 329}, {\"ngram\": \"his hands\", \"from\": 335, \"to\": 344}, {\"ngram\": \"his head\", \"from\": 357, \"to\": 365}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Finally, the numbers came up.\", \"from\": 367, \"to\": 396, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the numbers\", \"from\": 376, \"to\": 387}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lyles won in 9.784 seconds to edge out the Jamaican by five-thousandths of a tick of the clock.\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 492, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Lyles\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 402}, {\"ngram\": \"9.784 seconds\", \"from\": 410, \"to\": 423}, {\"ngram\": \"five-thousandths\", \"from\": 452, \"to\": 468}, {\"ngram\": \"a tick\", \"from\": 472, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"the clock\", \"from\": 482, \"to\": 491}]}, {\"sentence\": \"America's Fred Kerley came in third at 9.81.\", \"from\": 494, \"to\": 538,